      <steps class="- topic/ol task/steps ">
         <step id="AccProContDocFolder" class="- topic/li task/step ">
            <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">To access a <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Documents</uicontrol> folder at the project or contract level,  perform the following steps:</cmd>
            <substeps class="- topic/ol task/substeps ">
               <substep class="- topic/li task/substep ">
                  <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">In the module menu, click<uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Projects</uicontrol>.</cmd>
                  <info class="- topic/itemgroup task/info ">The<uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">PROJECTS</uicontrol> list page is displayed.</info>
               </substep>
               <substep class="- topic/li task/substep ">
                  <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">Select the appropriate project, and then click<uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">View</uicontrol>.</cmd>
                  <info class="- topic/itemgroup task/info ">The<uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">VIEW PROJECT</uicontrol>page is displayed.</info>
               </substep>
               <substep product="Include_for_1B_ACP" class="- topic/li task/substep ">
                  <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">In the navigation pane, expand the appropriate project folder, expand the <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Documents</uicontrol>folder,and then click the appropriate folder.</cmd>
               </substep>
               <substep product="Exclude_for_1B" class="- topic/li task/substep ">
                  <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">Inthe navigation pane, expand the appropriate project folder, and then perform either of the following steps:</cmd>
                  <info class="- topic/itemgroup task/info ">
                     <ul class="- topic/ul ">
                        <li class="- topic/li ">To access the<uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Documents</uicontrol> folder at the project level, click<uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Documents</uicontrol> or expand<uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Documents</uicontrol>, and then click the appropriate folder.<p class="- topic/p ">The <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">DOCUMENTS</uicontrol> list page is displayed.</p>
                        </li>
                        <li class="- topic/li ">To access the <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Documents</uicontrol> folder at the contract level, perform  the following steps: <ol class="- topic/ol ">
                              <li class="- topic/li ">Expand the<uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Contracts</uicontrol> folder.</li>
                              <li class="- topic/li ">Expand the appropriate contract folder, and then click<uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Documents</uicontrol> or expand <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Documents</uicontrol>, and click the appropriate folder.<p class="- topic/p ">The <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">DOCUMENTS</uicontrol> list page is displayed.</p>
